reviews.text: This is a great fast food service around the area. As soon as I entered, I immediately noticed how bright and clean the restaurant is, which created such a good first impression. I had the chicken chops (雞扒) for lunch and the dish was pretty delicious. If I'm ever in the area again, I'd be more than happy to come back for another visit!
Delicious food. Clean & nice environment. Good service.

Bit tricky to find as there’s no sign in English ( look for the red chicken logo and you’ll know you’ve arrived at the right place).

The food was very good and the price was great! 5/5
Restaurant and food are nice, but really strange and not eco-friendly to use disposable plastic cutlery and stirrers in the whole restaurant. 😑
The chicken filet is delicious

result.name: 榮式燒雞扒

reviews.text: 燒雞扒皮脆肉嫩😋

This is a great fast food service around the area. As soon as I entered, I immediately noticed how bright and clean the restaurant is, which created such a good first impression. I had the chicken chops (雞扒) for lunch and the dish was pretty delicious. If I'm ever in the area again, I'd be more than happy to come back for another visit!

招牌燒雞飯 雞腿肉外層烤的酥脆 一口咬下同時又能吃到雞肉紮實多汁口感～好吃

有一位店員讓我印象很深刻 點餐與送餐時親切帶著微笑 我在拍食物照時 還跑過來幫我把角度喬正，說：這樣拍更好看！（笑）

這趟來香港旅遊吃的第一餐 體驗很好～
第一次試呢間分店，十分失望。雞扒份量只有屯門店一半。 同一條街 仲有好多餐廳， 可免則免。
